            "title": "半日收市︱險守250天線 恒指半日跌幅收窄至312點報19815點 芯片股跑出",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">關稅戰烽煙處處，再為環球股市帶來動盪，港股今早也曾失守250天線，其後跌幅明顯收窄，芯片股更逆市揚升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"華虹半導體官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"華虹半導體官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">華虹半導體官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早甫開市即再失守二萬點關口，開報19494點、跌632點，早段曾進一步尋底並跌穿250天線(最新約為19491點)，低見19260點，挫867點，但未幾已於250天線失而復得，並一度重越二萬點，於早市中段升上半日高位20019點，僅跌108點，其後於19700點之上徘徊。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"華虹半導體官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"華虹半導體官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">華虹半導體官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"s