com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_source-web_中國石油5.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中國石油微博</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"華虹半導體官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">華虹半導體官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華潤萬象生活官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250224_FI_source-web_01209-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：華潤萬象生活官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國石油微博\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_source-web_中國石油5.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中國石油微博</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指中午收報19815點，跌312點或1.55%，較早市低位已跌少約64%。恒生科技指數半日跌43點或0.96%，報4524點；國企指數跌90點或1.22%，報7340點。主板半日成交2077.64億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日跌142點，報19776點，低水39點。科指期貨升17點，報4524點，低水1點。國指期貨跌15點，報7326點，低水14點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股暫仍跌多於升，芯片及半導體相關股應是最先跑出逆市報升的主要板塊。市場憧憬在中美關稅戰之下，國產芯片反而有機會進一步搶去海外芯片的生意，對內地芯片及半導體相關企業或危中有機。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯國際(00981)低開高走，最高曾見43.6元，飆11.37%；中午收報41.9元，升幅雖然收窄至7.02%，仍登上藍籌升幅榜首，半日成交達76.69億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華虹半導體(01347)也漲5.13%，報28.7元；上海復旦(01385)更升7.74%，報25.75元；英諾賽科(02577)逆市微升0.28%，報36.05元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一逆市受捧的板塊是內房及物管股，這類股份受關稅戰影響相對不明顯，加上在中央一系列政策支持下，一線與核心二線城市房地產市道似漸回穩，亦成為內房與物管股炒作的借口。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藍籌內房與物管股幾乎全線報升，華潤萬象生活(01209)升3.58%，報34.75元，是表現次佳的藍籌；同系華潤置地(01109)則跌0.21%，報24元。龍湖(00960)漲2.37%，報9.5元，；中國海外(00688)升2.55%，報12.86元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重債內房股炒作更烈，融創中國(01918)飆12.59%，報1.52元；世茂集團(00813)漲8.57%，報0.76元；旭輝(00884)升7.14%，報0.225元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：華潤萬象生活官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250224_FI_source-web_01209-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華潤萬象生活官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250224_FI_source-web_01209-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：華潤萬象生活官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於今早為恒指提供最多點數進賬的股份則是小米(01810)，該股於今早開市後不足20分鐘已開始倒升，最高曾衝上41.75元，升7.33%；中午收報40.05元，升幅收窄至2.96%，但仍是「ATMXJ」當中今早唯一逆市報升的股份，令恒指跌少逾33點，並以159.21億元交投成為主板股份成交額榜的冠軍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">而早市逆市報升的藍籌則合共12隻，除了上述提過的中芯、小米及3隻藍籌內房與物管股外，尚有內地消費股蒙牛乳業(02319)、農夫山泉(09633)、海底撈(06862)，逆市漲2.9%的內地電訊股中國聯通(00762)，以及新奧能源(02688)、信義玻璃(00868)、信義光能(00968)，升幅起碼也有0.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥股則沽壓較大，之前美國總統特朗普表示，將很快宣布一項重大的藥品進口關稅，以迫使藥廠離開中國，在美國建立生產基地，以便向國內市場銷售。有關說法成為藥股捱沽的原因之一。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥明康德(02359)表明擬進行2025年第2輪A股回購，該股今早在港仍明顯跑輸大市，收報46.45元，跌4.72%；藥明生物(02269)跌2.13%，報17.44元；翰森製藥(03692)也跌3.73%，報20.65元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">油價持續向下，「三桶油」縱有大股東增持與回購消息支持，今早股價依然再跌。中國石油(00857)跌5.48%，報5.17元；中海油(00883)跌2.23%，報15.78元；中國石化(00386)跌2.37%，報4.94元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國石油微博\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_source-web_中國石油5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國石油微博\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_source-web_中國石油5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國石油微博</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅金融股跌勢未止，友邦(01299)挫5.46%，報50.25元；滙控(00005)跌2.48%，報70.9元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「ATMXJ」中除了小米以外的4隻股份均續跌，阿里巴巴(09988)險守「紅底股」身份，收報100.4元，但仍跌2.05%；騰訊(00700)跌1.32%，報434.6元；美團(03690)跌1.14%，報139元；京東(09618)跌2.83%，報133.7元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">聯想(00992)則在藍籌中包尾，收跌6%，報7.05元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14841146-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e9%9a%aa%e5%ae%88250%e5%a4%a9%e7%b7%9a-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84%e8%87%b3312%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b119815",
