        {
            "title": "期指按金明起上調逾23%至49%   大期按金逾16萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期貨結算公司公布，恒生指數期貨按金將於4月10日(星期四)起大幅上調，升幅約49%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241009_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241009_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">俗稱「大期」的恒生指數期貨每張基本按金由109991元，大幅上調48.8%至163656元，維持按金由87992元升至130924元；「細期」、即小型指數期貨每張基本按金由21998元增至32731元，維持按金由17598元增至26184元，升幅同為48.9%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生中國企業指數每張基本按金由50207元增至63308元，維持按金由40165元增至50646元；小型恒生中國企業指數每張基本按金由10041元至12661元，維持按金由8032元增至10128元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數期每張基本按金由43264元，上調23.5%至53426元，維持按金由34611元增至42740元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14841046-%e6%9c%9f%e6%8c%87%e6%8c%89%e9%87%91%e6%98%8e%e8%b5%b7%e4%b8%8a%e8%aa%bf%e9%80%be23%e8%87%b349-%e5%a4%a7%e6%9c%9f%e6%8c%89%e9%87%91%e9%80%be16%e8%90%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-09 12:05:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
