            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股半日收升   軍工股上揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股半日跌轉升，兩市成交合計 10952.95億元(人民幣‧下同)，軍工股上揚。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指半日收報3152 點，升7點或0.24%，今早以3110點開市，跌35點或1.13%。低見3070，跌75點或2.38%，隨即跌幅收窄，最高見3155點，跌10點或0.32%，為上午高位，半日成交4823.78億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日收報9477點，升52點或0.56%，今日開市報9271點，亦跌153點或1.63%，早段最低見9119，挫305點或3.24%，為半日低位，其後向上，最高見9531，跌107點或1.14%，半日成交6129.25億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數半日報3662點，升11點或0.32%，今早跌44點或1.22%，開報3606點；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日升11點或0.61%，報1851點，今早開市報1805點，跌34點或1.89%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中美貿易戰如火如荼，滬深軍工股逆市拉升。中船防務(600685.SH)盈喜，料首季淨利潤升最多12倍，A股股價漲停，半日升10%，報23.43元 ; 煉石航空(000697.SZ)升10.01%，報7.69元; 愛樂達(300696.SZ)升停封板，半日升20.01%，報16.38元  ; 晨曦航空(300581.SZ)升20.02%，報10.19元，新余國科(300722.SZ)升20%，報29.16元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國海防(600764.SH)彈10.01%，報28.69元 ; 天海防務(300008.SZ)升 9.2%，報5.58元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14840857-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%87-%e8%bb%8d%e5%b7%a5%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%8a%e6%8f%9a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-09 11:40:57",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
